      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What is Jasper AI?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Jasper AI is an AI content marketing platform for generating on-brand copy across blog posts, ads, emails, social content, product descriptions, and video scripts. Its core differentiator is the Brand Voice feature, which analyzes your existing content to build a model of your brand's tone and style.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How much does Jasper AI cost?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Jasper AI Pro costs $69/seat/month on monthly billing or $59/seat/month billed annually. Business pricing is custom. The 7-day free trial requires a credit card. Note: the previously available Creator plan at $49/month was deprecated in 2024.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Is there a free version of Jasper AI?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">No permanent free plan. Jasper offers a 7-day credit-card-gated free trial on the Pro plan. Unlike Copy.ai, there is no free tier.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What is the Jasper AI Brand Voice feature?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Brand Voice analyzes your existing published content to build a model of your brand's tone, vocabulary, and sentence structure. Generated content then references this model to produce output consistent with your established style. The Pro plan includes 2 voices; Business includes unlimited.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Does Jasper AI do SEO?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Jasper has a Surfer SEO integration that shows live content scoring inside the editor — but this requires a separate Surfer SEO subscription ($119–$219/month). Without Surfer, Jasper has no native SEO optimization features.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Can Jasper AI publish to WordPress?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">No. Jasper AI cannot auto-publish to WordPress, Webflow, Ghost, or any other CMS. Every article requires manual upload and formatting.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Does Jasper AI do local SEO?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">No. Jasper completely lacks local SEO features — no Google Business Profile management, no local citation tools, no GBP post generation, and no Google Maps ranking features.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What is the 'Jasper Tax'?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
